```go
	"fmt"
	"golang.org/x/sys/unix"
)

func main() {
	// 获取内核版本信息
	version, err := unix.SysctlByName("kern.version")
	if err != nil {
		fmt.Println("Error getting kern.version:", err)
		return
	}
	fmt.Println("Kern.version:", version)

	// 获取主机名
	hostname, err := unix.SysctlByName("kern.hostname")
	if err != nil {
		fmt.Println("Error getting kern.hostname:", err)
		return
	}
	fmt.Println("Kern.hostname:", hostname)

	// 获取 CPU 数量
	ncpu, err := unix.SysctlByName("hw.ncpu")
	if err != nil {
		fmt.Println("Error getting hw.ncpu:", err)
		return
	}
	fmt.Println("HW.ncpu:", ncpu)
}
```
